
1. STRING Challenge 
 Problem: Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters 
Description: 
Given a string, find the length of the longest substring without repeating characters. 
Input: 
"abcabcbb" 

Code:
string = "abcabcbb" 
remove_duplicates = "".join(sorted(set(string)))
len_of_string = len(remove_duplicates)
print(f"Substring Characters : {remove_duplicates}")
print(f"Length of the Longest substring : {len_of_string}")

Output:
Substring Characters : abc
Length of the Longest substring : 3

